    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The town’s name changed to Belle Glade to honor its reputation as the “Belle of the Glades.”",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        10
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.bellegladechamber.com/our-history"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "In 1921, a research station was founded to grow crops on reclaimed Everglades land, later becoming the Everglades Experiment Station.",
